          "date": "2014-12-26 22:53:44.000000000",
          "tz": -300
        },
        "subject": "LU-6026 tests: modify sanity-sec to flush MDT locks",
        "message": "LU-6026 tests: modify sanity-sec to flush MDT locks\n\nIn order to create test directories, the test enables admin mode on\na client, and then disables it. It's possible that the client could\nthen start the nodemap test before the MDT has flushed all its locks.\nThis patch flushes the locks on the client after re-disabling admin\nmode, so that the proper mapping is guaranteed.\n\nSigned-off-by: Kit Westneat <kit.westneat@gmail.com>\nChange-Id: If0707cfc3e93b25538c11347d9d7a1178fcc151f\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
